23:01.020 --> 23:02.480
but you got to wait
till after I have him.

23:02.680 --> 23:03.480
No.

23:03.680 --> 23:07.210
It can't wait. Need it now.

23:08.660 --> 23:12.350
In that case,
I can give you a million.

23:12.550 --> 23:15.560
Look, you know what Teddy
did to me, okay?

23:15.760 --> 23:17.570
Why I'm after him
in the first fucking place.

23:17.770 --> 23:19.810
This is all I got, a million.
Take it or leave it.

23:20.010 --> 23:22.710
Okay, a million.

23:22.910 --> 23:24.740
- Good. Anything else?
- Yeah.

23:24.940 --> 23:27.850
I'm gonna need passports,
for me and my entire family.

23:28.050 --> 23:29.510
Can you help me?

23:29.710 --> 23:30.890
All right.

23:31.090 --> 23:32.680
Call this number.

23:32.880 --> 23:36.170
Guy called Top Notch will
answer. Tell him I sent you.

23:36.370 --> 23:38.170
Tell him I'm paying. All right?

23:38.370 --> 23:39.690
Okay.

23:39.890 --> 23:41.380
How soon can you move?

23:41.580 --> 23:44.520
As soon as I get
the documents and the money.

23:44.720 --> 23:46.420
You know it's not going
to be easy to find Teddy

23:46.620 --> 23:47.600
after last night, right?

23:47.800 --> 23:50.180
- I know.
- One more thing.

23:55.290 --> 23:57.050
I'm gonna need your word
that after you get

23:57.250 --> 23:58.710
what you need from Teddy
you're gonna kill him.

23:58.910 --> 24:00.780
No problem.

24:00.980 --> 24:03.300
I'm fucking serious, <i>moreno.</i>

24:03.500 --> 24:05.370
You could've left me
with those <i>vatos</i>and you didn't,

24:05.570 --> 24:07.130
so I trust you,
but this time, it's...

24:07.330 --> 24:10.410
it's-it's not only me,
it's my family, okay?

24:10.610 --> 24:13.690
Teddy cannot be alive to come
after us once I betray him.

24:16.100 --> 24:19.930
This is the easiest promise I'm
gonna make to you today, Oso.

24:21.420 --> 24:25.220
If you get me Teddy,
I'll kill that motherfucker.

24:26.220 --> 24:27.700
<i>A toda madre.</i>

24:33.050 --> 24:35.780
