24:43.130 --> 24:45.130
It's your turn.

24:48.890 --> 24:51.070
[sighs]

25:09.670 --> 25:12.160
Yeah, I know.

25:12.360 --> 25:14.960
I promised I'd visit more,
it's just...

25:15.160 --> 25:16.820
been a lot going on.

25:17.020 --> 25:19.310
After we ride,
I'll tell you all about it.

25:19.510 --> 25:21.340
Yeah?

25:23.480 --> 25:25.590
[sighs]

25:32.350 --> 25:34.840
Y'all hang back, yeah?

25:35.040 --> 25:36.840
Let's go, baby.

25:39.290 --> 25:41.460
[horse whinnies]

25:45.160 --> 25:47.160
