25:56.060 --> 25:57.170
[grunts]

25:59.830 --> 26:01.970
Shit. Oh, shit.

26:16.360 --> 26:17.990
For Leon?

26:18.190 --> 26:20.020
Uh-huh.

26:20.220 --> 26:22.030
