where the car is?

26:32.030 --> 26:34.420
108th and Fig. A Chevelle.

26:34.620 --> 26:36.660
[pager beeping]

26:44.700 --> 26:47.050
[line ringing]

26:47.250 --> 26:49.540
<i>KANE:</i>
<i>Do you fish, Frankie?</i>

26:49.740 --> 26:50.710
No.

26:50.910 --> 26:52.060
<i>KANE:</i>
<i>Well, I do.</i>

26:52.260 --> 26:53.880
And I caught something big.

26:54.080 --> 26:55.200
[chuckles]

26:55.400 --> 26:58.610
<i>2376 Alameda.</i>

27:00.270 --> 27:01.720
Come and see.

27:02.720 --> 27:04.200
[line clicks]

27:24.390 --> 27:26.430
[Kane chuckles]

27:36.300 --> 27:37.760
[chuckles]

27:37.960 --> 27:41.650
