just walk out that door?

27:58.430 --> 28:00.640
[garage door opening]

28:03.850 --> 28:07.510
KANE:
You know, when I woke up
this morning,

28:07.710 --> 28:10.820
my girl was threatening
to move back to Vallejo.

28:13.860 --> 28:17.000
I begged her to move here
after my bid.

28:17.200 --> 28:18.930
Said it was safe.

28:20.000 --> 28:23.350
So, we get to arguing
and shit, right?

28:23.550 --> 28:27.280
Because now,
I'm looking like a liar.

28:28.390 --> 28:32.640
Used to be, days like this,

28:32.840 --> 28:35.150
