28:43.020 --> 28:45.340
that I loved her.

28:45.540 --> 28:49.170
But this argument...

28:49.370 --> 28:53.310
kept going on and on...

28:53.510 --> 28:57.490
all because of you...

28:58.700 --> 29:00.970
...and a fucking cop.

29:03.840 --> 29:05.330
Don't you...

29:05.530 --> 29:07.980
