29:33.870 --> 29:36.120
[grunts]

29:36.320 --> 29:37.190
[Kane chuckles]

29:37.390 --> 29:39.360
[Louie groans]

29:40.600 --> 29:41.880
[grunting]

29:45.050 --> 29:47.710
[Kane chuckling]

29:47.910 --> 29:49.370
[sobbing]

29:49.570 --> 29:51.920
Oh, look at that.

29:52.120 --> 29:53.200
Mm.

29:55.230 --> 29:56.860
Look at that.

29:57.890 --> 29:59.270
[panting]

30:10.080 --> 30:11.770
Stay put.

30:15.950 --> 30:17.770
[sniffles]

30:20.090 --> 30:22.090
[sobs]

30:30.480 --> 30:33.410
[gate screeching]

30:56.540 --> 30:59.030
I've got a gun
and I'm not giving it up.

30:59.230 --> 31:00.650
Kane asked me to come.

31:00.850 --> 31:03.650
I walk in or I leave. Your call.

31:09.140 --> 31:11.140
[train whistle blowing]

31:16.630 --> 31:18.630
[hip-hop music playing]

31:29.190 --> 31:30.330
ANT:
Hey.

31:41.650 --> 31:43.690
They in there.

31:45.830 --> 31:47.830
You straight, homie?

31:54.220 --> 31:56.150
[Kane chuckles]

31:59.050 --> 32:02.190
Yo, the stables was a lick,
my nigga.

32:02.390 --> 32:04.670
FRANKLIN:
Yeah, I can see that.

32:07.400 --> 32:09.060
What you need me here for?

32:09.260 --> 32:12.160
Well, once I get what I need...

32:14.200 --> 32:16.070
