to do the honors.

32:18.690 --> 32:20.350
Take her out.

32:20.550 --> 32:22.350
Nah.

32:23.420 --> 32:25.560
That's all you.

32:25.760 --> 32:27.870
KANE:
Ever tell you my people
were from...

32:28.070 --> 32:30.530
Allensworth?

32:30.730 --> 32:33.050
Black farmers.

32:34.050 --> 32:36.120
So, the water got bad.

32:36.320 --> 32:39.060
Lost a lot of ranchers, so...

32:39.260 --> 32:41.060
one summer...

32:43.580 --> 32:47.550
...Grandpa said that
I had to brand the cows.

32:47.750 --> 32:50.280
I was like, nine, ten,

32:50.480 --> 32:53.490
crying and shit. [chuckles]

32:53.690 --> 32:56.250
'Cause, you know,
I didn't want to hurt them.

32:56.450 --> 32:58.320
But he said...

32:58.520 --> 33:01.390
the farm was how
we protect our family,

33:01.590 --> 33:03.320
that the farm...

33:03.520 --> 33:06.630
is how we protect
our livelihood.

33:08.950 --> 33:10.430
A legacy.

33:10.630 --> 33:12.570
To take pride in that.

33:23.340 --> 33:25.100
So I did.

33:30.310 --> 33:32.970
Branded...

33:33.170 --> 33:35.800
every cow...

33:36.000 --> 33:39.770
with my head held high.
[chuckles]

33:53.650 --> 33:56.610
You know what I want.

34:06.620 --> 34:08.520
[laughing]

34:14.980 --> 34:17.810
[screaming]

34:25.020 --> 34:27.640
You still don't want
to talk, Louie?

34:30.510 --> 34:31.510
Okay.

34:33.200 --> 34:35.200
[screaming]

34:48.870 --> 34:50.880
KANE:
Tough one, huh?

34:51.080 --> 34:53.050
See I'm gonna have
to break you down.

34:53.250 --> 34:56.050
Got a lot of niggas fresh out.

34:58.400 --> 35:00.680
Love feisty red bones like you.

35:01.750 --> 35:03.850
[Kane laughs]

35:07.550 --> 35:10.720
Guess we having ourselves
a little party.

35:12.900 --> 35:14.690
[chuckling]

35:16.070 --> 35:20.870
Hey. Call Percy, tell him I got
a business proposition for him.

35:21.070 --> 35:24.220
Damn, she bad.

35:24.420 --> 35:26.260
Get Ricky's ass over here, too.

35:26.460 --> 35:28.190
You mind?

35:29.260 --> 35:30.610
KANE:
Yeah, nigga, do your thing.

35:30.810 --> 35:32.230
Come on, Indiana.

35:32.430 --> 35:34.190
[breathing shakily]

35:39.720 --> 35:41.440
[Louie exhales]

35:51.450 --> 35:53.280
FRANKLIN:
Give up Buckley.

35:54.320 --> 35:56.800
And pray for a quick death.

35:58.290 --> 36:01.120
Because what these niggas plan
to do to you...

36:01.320 --> 36:03.610
