36:03.810 --> 36:05.810
Franklin...

36:08.950 --> 36:11.580
...you did this to me.

36:11.780 --> 36:13.610
Oh, yeah?

36:21.280 --> 36:22.800
Fine.

36:23.000 --> 36:25.250
You want Teddy?

36:26.660 --> 36:28.110
I'll help you.

36:30.110 --> 36:32.150
Sorry, Louie.

36:33.490 --> 36:36.150
I already got an in.

36:40.470 --> 36:41.510
[door opens]

36:41.710 --> 36:43.160
- [door closes]
- [sobbing]

36:52.790 --> 36:54.830
