37:10.840 --> 37:12.980
[sighs]

37:14.330 --> 37:15.640
Fuck.

37:22.580 --> 37:24.340
[pager beeping]

37:26.860 --> 37:28.830
[baby crying in distance]

37:32.000 --> 37:33.730
[trunk lid shuts]

37:35.520 --> 37:37.080
Come on.

37:37.280 --> 37:39.840
[pager beeping]

37:45.670 --> 37:47.190
[sighs]

37:48.570 --> 37:50.260
- RENNY: Project counsel?
- Got a problem,

37:50.460 --> 37:52.300
they bring it to whoever
we elect for that.

37:52.500 --> 37:55.200
They squash it.
That way, we govern ourselves.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.580
You gonna do this
before or after

37:56.780 --> 37:58.200
you resupply the cook houses?

37:58.400 --> 38:00.070
We need rules
and regulations first.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.550
RENNY:
Lee, we need everyone

38:01.750 --> 38:03.760
on a full stomach.
Then they gonna listen.

38:03.960 --> 38:06.380
What I'm not about to do is have
chaos up in this motherfucker.

38:06.580 --> 38:08.390
I just got to handle
this shit first.

38:08.590 --> 38:09.900
WANDA:
Leon!

38:10.100 --> 38:11.910
Franklin's on the phone,
he sound stressed.

38:12.110 --> 38:13.590
All right.

38:15.390 --> 38:16.940
<i>FRANKLIN:</i>
<i>Leon.</i>

38:18.290 --> 38:19.910
Yeah, I got you,
but I can't guarantee

38:20.110 --> 38:21.330
he'll hit me back, though.

38:21.530 --> 38:23.260
Look, just keep paging him 911
until he does, okay?

38:23.460 --> 38:24.920
<i>LEON:</i>
<i>Then what?</i>

38:25.120 --> 38:27.750
Ain't much I can say to make
sure he call you if he does.

38:27.950 --> 38:29.890
There is.

38:32.100 --> 38:34.310
I'll bring a goddamn calvary.

38:34.510 --> 38:36.590
Give me the fucking address,
Leon!

38:36.790 --> 38:39.590
1625 Duarte Street.
I'll be right there.

38:44.830 --> 38:47.420
[dialing]

38:50.320 --> 38:52.390
[pager beeping]

38:54.460 --> 38:56.470
[pager beeping]

39:00.610 --> 39:03.090
[beeping fades, echoing]

39:05.680 --> 39:08.100
SKULLY:
What's up, G?

39:11.270 --> 39:12.350
