39:25.700 --> 39:27.670
- Yeah, we all did something.
- [tires screeching]

39:33.360 --> 39:34.990
Bitch nigga!

39:35.990 --> 39:38.340
The hell is this?

39:38.540 --> 39:39.650
Where the fuck she at?!

39:39.850 --> 39:41.200
