I'm the one that dimed them out

39:47.750 --> 39:49.830
and I'll be fucking dead.
Now you want to yell and scream?

39:50.030 --> 39:52.970
Or you want to do shit
the right way and survive?

39:55.520 --> 39:58.190
You can kill me if you want to.

39:58.390 --> 40:00.670
Or we can stop wasting time
and save your wife

40:00.870 --> 40:03.840
from what them jailhouse niggas
plan to do to her.

40:13.510 --> 40:15.000
It's knowledge right here,
homie.

40:15.200 --> 40:16.690
Man, fuck that book.

40:16.890 --> 40:19.860
There's weed, drink,
and a bitch in there.

40:20.060 --> 40:21.690
But you out here with me.

40:21.890 --> 40:22.760
You a simp, homie.

40:22.960 --> 40:24.520
Who want to run a train

40:24.720 --> 40:26.700
on a ho that's crying and shit?

40:26.900 --> 40:28.870
Shit, me and every nigga here.

40:29.070 --> 40:30.520
[chuckling]:
I ain't fucking with you.

40:33.700 --> 40:36.190
[hip-hop music
playing on stereo]

40:36.390 --> 40:38.360
What's going on in here?

40:39.530 --> 40:41.020
Oh.

40:43.540 --> 40:45.370
- Okay.
- Mm-hmm.

40:45.570 --> 40:49.720
Nice little red bone. Hmm.

40:49.920 --> 40:52.900
Yeah, there might be room
on the track,

40:53.100 --> 40:55.030
if that monkey talking.

40:56.240 --> 40:59.760
